L '''senhal d'ajuda''' ó tamien '''senhal de bioléncia doméstica''' ye un géstio dua mano que puode ser ousado por un andibíduo para alertar ls outros de qu'el se sente amenaçado i percisa d'ajuda por meio dua chamada de bídeo ó pessonalmente.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brooke |first1=Bobb |title="Signal for Help" Is a New Tool for Abuse Victims During the Coronavirus Lockdown and Beyond |url=https://www.vogue.com/article/signal-for-help-womens-funding-network-abuse-coronavirus |accessdate=6 de maio de 2020 |work=Vogue |date=28 de abril de 2020}}</ref> Fui ouriginalmente criado cumo ua ferramienta para cumbater l'oumiento de ls causos de bioléncia doméstica an to l mundo cumo resultado de las medidas d'outo-eisolamiento relacionadas a la pandemia de COBID-19.<ref>{{cite news |first1=Emma |last1=Graham-Harrison |first2=Helena |last2=Smith |first3=Liz |last3=Ford |title=Lockdowns around the world bring rise in domestic violence |url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2020/mar/28/lockdowns-world-rise-domestic-violence |accessdate=6 de maio de 2020 |work=The Guardian |date=28 de márcio de 2020}}</ref>

L senhal ye rializado segurando a mano para cima cul polegar anfiado na palma de a mano i, an seguida, dobrando ls dedos para baixo, prendendo simbolicamente l polegar antre ls dedos.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Nadia |first1=Ebrahim |title=This Secret Signal Could Help Women In Lockdown With Their Abusers |url=https://www.refinery29.com/en-ca/2020/04/9699234/domestic-violence-quarantine-coronavirus-signal-help |accessdate=6 de maio de 2020 |publisher=Refinery29 |date=22 de abril de 2020}}</ref> Fui antencionalmente porjetado cumo un único mobimiento de mano cuntino, an beç dun senhal mantido nua posiçon, que poderie ser facilmente besible.

L Senhal de Ajuda fui apersentado pula purmeira beç ne l [[Canadá]] pula Canadian Women's Foundation an 14 d'abril de 2020,<ref>{{cite news |title=Signal for Help Campaign Launches to Help People Experiencing Gender-Based Violence During Home Isolation |url=https://www.mcgill.ca/definetheline/channels/news/signal-help-campaign-launches-help-people-experiencing-gender-based-violence-during-home-isolation-321629 |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020 |publisher=McGill |date=14 de abril de 2020}}</ref> i an 28 d'abril de 2020 ne ls [[Stados Ounidos]] pula Women's Funding Network (WFN). Recebiu eilogios generalizados d'ourganizaçones d'amboras locales,<ref>{{cite news |title=Self-Isolation Is Fuelling a Rise in Gender-Based Violence |url=https://www.ellecanada.com/culture/society/self-isolation-is-fuelling-a-rise-in-gender-based-violence |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020 |work=Elle Canada |date=14 de abril de 2020}}</ref> nacionales<ref>{{cite news |last1=Alexandra |first1=Jardine |title=This simple hand signal sends an alert about domestic abuse during the coronavirus crisis |url=https://adage.com/creativity/work/womens-funding-network-canadian-womens-foundation-signal-help/2254366 |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020 |work=AdAge |date=4 de maio de 2020}}</ref> i anternacionales<ref>{{cite news |last1=Midori |first1=Aoki |title=『家にとどまって』 ～その家が安全ではなかったら？～ |url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200420/k10012396031000.html |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020 |publisher=NHK |date=20 de abril de 2020}}</ref> por ajudar a fornecer ua soluçon moderna pa l'oumiento de ls causos de bioléncia doméstica.

L senhal fui reconhecido por mais de 40 ourganizaçones ne l [[Canadá]] i ne ls [[Stados Ounidos]] cumo ua ferramienta útele para ajudar a cumbater la bioléncia doméstica.<ref>{{cite news |first1=Wendy |last1=Gillis |first2=Alyshah |last2=Hasham |title= Are you a victim of violence at home? Here's how to get help amid COVID-19 |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2020/04/22/are-you-a-victim-of-violence-at-home-heres-how-to-get-help-amid-covid-19.html |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020|work=Toronto Star |date=22 de abril de 2020}}</ref>

Abordando las preocupaçones de que ls abusadores puodan tomar coincimiento de tal eniciatiba online generalizada, la Canadian Women's Foundation i outras ourganizaçones sclarecírun qu'esse senhal nun ye "algo que bai salbar l die", mas si ua ferramienta qu'alguien poderie ousar para oubter ajuda.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jonathan |first1=Forani |title=Code words, hand signals and social media: How attempts to help abuse victims might backfire |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/code-words-hand-signals-and-social-media-how-attempts-to-help-abuse-victims-might-backfire-1.4899062 |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020 |publisher=CTV News Toronto |date=16 de abril de 2020}}</ref>

Anstruçones subre l que fazer se un andibíduo benir l senhal i cumo fazer l check-in cun sigurança tamien fúrun criadas.<ref>{{cite web |title=Signal for Help |url=https://canadianwomen.org/signal-for-help/ |website=The Canadian Women's Foundation |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Signal for Help |url=https://www.womensfundingnetwork.org/signalforhelp/ |website=Women's Funding Network |accessdate=7 de maio de 2020}}</ref>

